        ... ‚â§ ‚à•f‚à• * (N * ‚à•e x‚à•) : mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_left (h_e x) (norm_nonneg _)
        ... ‚â§ N * ‚à•f‚à• * ‚à•e x‚à• : by rw [mul_comm ‚ÜëN ‚à•f‚à•, mul_assoc] } },
  { have he : ‚àÄ x : E, x = 0,
